    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a recipe content generator for a food blog called LowKeyCooking. Your job is to output a single, complete recipe in markdown format — nothing else. Do not include any explanation, intro text, or commentary before or after the markdown. Output only the raw markdown file content, starting with ---.\n\nGenerate a complete recipe markdown file for: {{ $json.recipe_name }}\n\nThe output must follow this exact structure:\n\n<!-- filename: [recipe-name-lowercase-hyphens.md] -->\n---\ntitle: [Full recipe name]\ndescription: [One sentence — appetizing, specific, max 20 words]\nimage: {{ $json.image_url }}\nprep_time: [e.g. 15 mins]\ncook_time: [e.g. 30 mins]\nservings: [e.g. 4]\nutensils:\n  - name: [Utensil 1]\n    url: https://www.amazon.com/s?k=[utensil+name+url+encoded]\n  - name: [Utensil 2]\n    url: https://www.amazon.com/s?k=[utensil+name+url+encoded]\n  - name: [Utensil 3]\n    url: https://www.amazon.com/s?k=[utensil+name+url+encoded]\n  - name: [Utensil 4]\n    url: https://www.amazon.com/s?k=[utensil+name+url+encoded]\nnutrition:\n  calories: [number only, no units]\n  protein: [e.g. 12g]\n  carbs: [e.g. 34g]\n  fat: [e.g. 14g]\n  fiber: [e.g. 3g]\n  sugar: [e.g. 5g]\n  sodium: [e.g. 480mg]\n---\n\n## Ingredients\n\n- [Quantity + ingredient]\n- [Quantity + ingredient]\n[list all ingredients, one per line]\n\n## Instructions\n\n1. [Clear, specific step]\n2. [Clear, specific step]\n[number all steps, one action per step]\n\nRules:\n- Filename must be the recipe name in lowercase with spaces replaced by hyphens (e.g. pulled-pork-tacos.md)\n- The image URL has already been provided above — use it exactly as given, do not modify it\n- Utensil URLs must use Amazon search format: https://www.amazon.com/s?k=search+terms\n- Include 4–6 utensils actually used in the recipe\n- Nutrition values should be realistic estimates per serving\n- Ingredients must include quantities and units\n- Instructions must be numbered, clear, and written in second person (\"Add the flour...\", not \"You should add...\")\n- Do not include any text outside the markdown content\n- The file must have valid YAML frontmatter — use exact 2-space indentation for list items"
      },
      "id": "f1432712-f1e0-4360-b602-26beac5fa7d6",
      "name": "Generate Recipe EN2",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.4,
      "position": [
        -3808,
